		<div class="quote"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Broken_Hill_Xplorer" title="Broken Hill Xplorer">This once-weekly train offers a great affordable and scenic way to travel across the state of New South Wales, from the state capital of Sydney to the small outback mining town of Broken Hill.</a></div>
